Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.92,0:27:17.86,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\bord14}After half a lifetime, you find a kindred spirit. The one who sat still is deeply moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.90,0:27:17.86,Song,,0,0,0,,{\k68}Bàn {\k56}shēng {\k29}yù {\k53}zhī {\k197}jǐ, {\k55}zhé {\k54}rén{\k47}gǎn {\k48}xìng {\k29}shēn
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.17,0:27:26.24,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\bord14}In the morrow, you took your sword and followed a worthy ruler.
