Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.81,0:28:41.84,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\bord14}The path marked by Heaven ever-changing, as fate is hard to discern.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.81,0:28:41.84,Song,,0,0,0,,{\k63}Tiān{\k50}dào {\k48}cháng{\k50}biàn {\k92}yì,{\k60} yùn {\k52}shù {\k100}yǎo {\k102}nán {\k66}xún{\k0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.98,0:28:51.26,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\bord14}Victory and defeat depends on guile and sincere vow for undying loyalty.
