Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.53,0:31:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Switch formations.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.56,0:31:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.18,0:31:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Acquiring your services is akin to a fish that gets water, {\i1}Strategos.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.18,0:31:45.82,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: Zhuge Liang's initial rank was "Strategist-General of the Household" (军师中郎将); \Nan idiosyncratic title invented by Liu Bei.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.47,0:31:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.06,0:31:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You are hard at work, {\i1}Strategos{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.17,0:31:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,After you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.98,0:32:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, these fresh recruits still need training. Only then can they fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.92,0:32:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Without training, a hundred men are only as good as one —
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.50,0:32:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,— but with proper drilling one man can equal a hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.33,0:32:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent. You've been working hard planning tactics and training our forces, {\i1}Strategos{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.40,0:32:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,For your hard-work, I personally weaved this hat as a token of my appreciation.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.37,0:32:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, don't you have lofty aspirations?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.79,0:32:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Weaving hats is but a petty diversion.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.65,0:32:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be so ungrateful?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.21,0:32:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My elder brother has worked hard day and night.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.95,0:32:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He made you this hat personally, but this is how you thank him!?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.96,0:32:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand your good intentions, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.09,0:32:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,However, since I left the mountains I have worked to accomplish your grand design.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.16,0:32:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Not for a moment have I forgotten your aspirations.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.50,0:32:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Our current situation is as unstable as a pile of eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.44,0:33:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you too can understand my view, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.08,0:33:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand your concerns, {\i1}Strategos{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.22,0:33:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I also worry about the generals of Cáo Cāo.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.59,0:33:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not fear, my lord. \NPlease, let us inspect Bowang-Slope.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.90,0:33:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,'Bowang-Slope'?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.40,0:33:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If Cao's forces were to arrive, they'd come directly to Xinye. What would they do at Bowang Slope?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.92,0:33:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Clearly, he just wants to enjoy the nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.93,0:33:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.48,0:33:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Before us stands Bowang Slope.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.81,0:34:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, Bowang Slope has many trees and bushes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.38,0:34:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If Cáo Cāo's troops arrive, we will lead them to the gorge
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.28,0:34:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and attack them with fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.32,0:34:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us keep surveying the terrain ahead, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.61,0:34:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.63,0:34:33.50,Thinking,,0,0,0,,After the {\i1}death of Sun Ce, Sun Quan inherited his brother's territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.53,0:34:37.04,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He guarded Jiangdong, while recruiting talented men from all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.50,0:34:39.77,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Cáo Cāo, in order to control Jiangdong —
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.87,0:34:44.88,Thinking,,0,0,0,,— had ordered Sun Quan to send his son to serve the sovereign, intending to hold him hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.88,0:34:44.82,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,420,4000,4420)\pos(1197.36,593.583)}Sūn Quán \NStyled: Zhòngmóu
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.91,0:34:47.00,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sun Quan refused.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.48,0:34:50.48,Thinking,,0,0,0,,After this, Cáo Cāo had intentions to march south.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.72,0:34:51.72,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,420,4000,4420)\pos(1215.36,714.766)}Huáng Gài \NStyled: Gōngfù
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.28,0:34:55.88,Thinking,,0,0,0,,In the spring of thirteenth year of the Jian'an era —
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.40,0:34:55.79,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,{\pos(1409.999,20)}Note: Year 208
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.00,0:35:02.43,Thinking,,0,0,0,,— Sun Quan complied with his mother, Dowager Wú's will to avenge Sun Jian.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.52,0:35:05.83,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He marched against Liú Biao's officer, Huáng Zǔ.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.97,0:35:11.20,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He stationed his troops in the county of Cháisāng and seeked to take the lands of Jīng.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.48,0:35:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sun Quan of Wú has killed Huang Zu and taken Xiàkǒu.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.45,0:35:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now he's camped at Chaisang \Nand surely covets Jīng-Province.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.79,0:35:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Liú Biao is bedridden with illness —
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.46,0:35:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,— and his son, {\i1}Liú Qi,{\i0} is incompetent and ignorant. He won't accomplish anything of note.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.83,0:35:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Liú Bèi, however, took refuge under Liú Biao after his defeat in Runan —
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.70,0:35:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,— and likely conspires to take over Jīng-Province. Since the time is right —
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.91,0:35:52.65,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,420,4000,4420)\pos(986.905,614.628)}Cáo Cāo \NStyled: Mèngdé
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.23,0:35:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,— wouldn't surely he take this opportunity to act?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.71,0:35:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He's now stationed in a tiny place like Xinye —
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.48,0:35:58.32,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(485.088,618.901)}Xú Shù \NStyled: Yuánzhí
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.44,0:35:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,— recruiting troops and accumulating provisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.00,0:36:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,One can easily see he has wild ambitions of hegemony.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.36,0:36:01.50,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(409.86,755.72)}Xún Yù\NStyled: Wénruò
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.20,0:36:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I will march once again before he can spread his wings! There cannot be any delay!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.70,0:36:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I have recently heard Liú Bèi acquired the services of a strategist named {\i1}Zhūgě Liàng.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.81,0:36:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of man is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.00,0:36:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,With the composed surname {\i1}Zhūgě{\i0} and the name{\i1} Liàng{\i0} —
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.22,0:36:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,he is of about twenty-six\N or twenty-seven years of age.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.76,0:36:50.00,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,420,4800,5020)\pos(267.633,748.538)}Xiàhóu Dūn \NStyled: Yuánràng
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.66,0:36:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now a whelp is his strategist? \NSeems Liú Bèi has ran out of personnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.24,0:36:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuánzhí.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.48,0:36:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Chancellor?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.08,0:37:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Zhūgě Liàng an acquaintance of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.09,0:37:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He is. His style name is Kǒngmíng and people call him 'the Sleeping Dragon'.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.00,0:37:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How is his ability compared to yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.70,0:37:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare I compare myself to Zhūgě Liàng?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.07,0:37:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I am as dim as the light of a firefly, but Zhūgě Liàng's brilliance is like that of the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.00,0:37:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor, Zhūgě Liàng has the talent to take Heaven and Earth and can turn the tide of the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.58,0:37:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Gods and spirits cannot fathom his plans \Nand he conceals the ambitions of Heaven and Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.16,0:37:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a genius of our age.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.10,0:38:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Liú Bèi has always held the ambitions of {\i1}a kūnpéng.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.10,0:38:02.63,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: A kūnpéng refers to a legendary roc, a giant bird of prey transformed from a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.45,0:38:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Zhūgě Liàng is to him like water is to a fish. It's like giving wings to a Tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.61,0:38:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid... I'm afraid none under Heaven can rival him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.00,0:38:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Xu Yuanzhi! Don't spout nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.92,0:38:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhūgě Liàng is as insignificant as a blade of grass. \NWhat's there to fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.83,0:38:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, General Xiahou. Yuanzhi is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.56,0:38:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Liú Bèi is a hero and now he has Zhūgě Liàng in his service. We must not underestimate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.61,0:38:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Liú Bèi is just a rat! I'll take him alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.24,0:38:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well! Remember the army is not a place for jests.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.18,0:38:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave a pledge if necessary. I will capture Liú Bèi and Zhūgě Liàng alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.00,0:38:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If I fail, I'll gladly give my head to the Chancellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.00,0:38:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.56,0:38:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I name Xiahou Dun as {\i1}Field-Marshal.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.83,0:38:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yú Jìn, Lǐ Diǎn {\i0} and {\i1}Hán Hào{\i0} will be his deputy officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.23,0:39:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Gather 100,000 troops and aim straight for Xinye.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.54,0:39:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.54,0:39:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.54,0:39:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood!
